AssertionError: expected is "Departing and Returning field cannot be empty.", but actual is "Sorry, there are no more seats available."
assert 'Sorry, there...ts available.' == 'Departing an...not be empty.'
  
  - Departing and Returning field cannot be empty.
  + Sorry, there are no more seats available.

AssertionError: expected is "Call now on 0800 MARSAIR to book!", but actual is "Sorry, code   is not valid"
assert 'Sorry, code   is not valid' == 'Call now on ...SAIR to book!'
  
  - Call now on 0800 MARSAIR to book!
  + Sorry, code   is not valid

AssertionError: expected is "Sorry, code XX0-XXX-000 is not valid", but actual is "Promotional code XX0-XXX-000 used: 00% discount!"
assert 'Promotional ...00% discount!' == 'Sorry, code ... is not valid'
  
  - Sorry, code XX0-XXX-000 is not valid
  + Promotional code XX0-XXX-000 used: 00% discount!

AssertionError: expected is "Promotional code XX5-XXX-005 used: 50% discount!", but actual is "Promotional code   XX5-XXX-005    used: 00% discount!"
assert 'Promotional ...00% discount!' == 'Promotional ...50% discount!'
  
  - Promotional code XX5-XXX-005 used: 50% discount!
  ?                                    ^
  + Promotional code   XX5-XXX-005    used: 00% discount!
  ?                 ++             +++      ^

AssertionError: expected is "Unfortunately, this schedule is not possible. Please try again.", but actual is "Sorry, there are no more seats available."
assert 'Sorry, there...ts available.' == 'Unfortunatel...se try again.'
  
  - Unfortunately, this schedule is not possible. Please try again.
  + Sorry, there are no more seats available.
